<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>               What:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> Lord Nagafen<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>               When:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> Sunday, June 9th, forming groups at noon EDT (US Eastern) - should finish up around 4 or 5 PM.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>               Who:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> Now open, originally Random Acts and invited guests from our usual pool of friends; raid force capped at 42 people (7 groups), maximum of 12 53+.  Dragon kill itself is levels 42-52, clerics from 39+ with 100+ MR and FR.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>               Where:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> Meeting at the Lavastorm rings<br>
